summary:
Custom file configuration (refer to 27084-TODO1);
Located in the sandbox's root directory, within the xgConfig folder, there is a config.txt file;
Utilizes a dictionary to write configuration files, enabling real-time value changes during HE operation for altering its behavior;
Responds to configuration file updates every round in the HE system.

